---
title: Spiced Chicken Empanadas  with Charred Corn Salsa
description: We've taken the best of an empanada; flavourful chicken in a transcendent pastry! Our pre-made dough is easy to use with a simple fill, gather, pinch, and bake technique. Served with sweet and crunchy corn and bell pepper salsa, we've got dinner covered!
